    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303720/extras/Logo.png?t=1763596373\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boot up your old computer and uncover a world <strong>like no other</strong>. The Motherboard is waiting, are you ready to Cheat and Glitch your way to the top?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303720/extras/glitch.png?t=1763596373\" /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Show Your Skill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your strongest troops in card form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IMG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from more than <strong>100 unique cards</strong> to build your army and assemble the strongest deck thanks to an array of powerful characters and magics,       or go with the flow of a <strong>pre-made strategy</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Optimize Your Tactics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Motherboard is home to many unusual peoples and monsters, each with their own special abilities and approach to battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IMG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
